OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775559585
OL,3,CWireless tickets to go on sale after
OL,4,Cpromoter defends Kanye West appearance
OL,6,FWireless Festival tickets are to go on
OL,7,Fsale as its promoter defended Kanye
OL,8,FWest's planned performance, after
OL,9,Fcalls for him to be barred from
OL,10,Fentering the UK because of
OL,11,Fantisemitism.
OL,13,FThe rapper, who is also known as Ye,
OL,14,Fis to top the bill for all three
OL,15,Fnights of the festival in London's
OL,16,FFinsbury Park in July.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775559585
OL,3,CWireless tickets to go on sale after
OL,4,Cpromoter defends Kanye West appearance
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,7,Fcalled the decision "deeply
OL,8,Fconcerning", while major sponsors have
OL,9,Fwithdrawn their support for the
OL,10,Ffestival because of the booking.
OL,12,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood has
OL,13,Ffaced calls from politicians and the
OL,14,FCampaign Against Antisemitism (CAA) to
OL,15,Fban West from coming to the UK, saying
OL,16,Fhis presence would not be "conducive
OL,17,Fto the public good".
OL,19,FThe Press Association understands that
OL,20,FWest's permission to enter the UK is
OL,21,Fcurrently being reviewed by ministers.
OL,26,@oD@UOUpD@KO]xD@[OUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
