OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775559585
OL,3,CWireless tickets to go on sale after
OL,4,Cpromoter defends Kanye West appearance
OL,6,FPresale tickets for Wireless Festival
OL,7,Fare released at 12pm on Tuesday, and
OL,8,Fthe general sale opens at 12pm on
OL,9,FWednesday.
OL,11,FMelvin Benn, managing director at
OL,12,FFestival Republic, which promotes
OL,13,FWireless Festival, described himself
OL,14,Fas a "deeply committed anti-fascist"
OL,15,Fand "person of forgiveness".
OL,26,@vD@FOUvD@dO]wD@EOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
