OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775559585
OL,3,CWireless tickets to go on sale after
OL,4,Cpromoter defends Kanye West appearance
OL,6,FIn a statement, Mr Benn added: "What
OL,7,FYe has said in the past about Jews and
OL,8,FHitler is as abhorrent to me as it is
OL,9,Fto the Jewish community, the Prime
OL,10,FMinister and others that have
OL,11,Fcommented and ` taking him at his word
OL,12,F` to Ye now also.
OL,14,F"Ye's music is played on commercial
OL,15,Fradio stations in this country. It is
OL,16,Favailable via live streams and
OL,17,Fdownloads in this country without
OL,18,Fcomment or vitriol from anyone and he
OL,19,Fhas a legal right to come into the
OL,20,Fcountry and to perform in this country.
OL,26,@nD@`OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775559585
OL,3,CWireless tickets to go on sale after
OL,4,Cpromoter defends Kanye West appearance
OL,6,F"He is intended to come in and
OL,7,Fperform. We are not giving him a
OL,8,Fplatform to extol opinion of whatever
OL,9,Fnature, only to perform the songs that
OL,10,Fare currently played on the radio
OL,11,Fstations in our country and the
OL,12,Fstreaming platforms in our country and
OL,13,Flistened to and enjoyed by millions."
OL,15,FThe president of the Board of Deputies
OL,16,Fof British Jews said it was "time for
OL,17,FWireless to do the decent thing and
OL,18,Frescind an invitation they never
OL,19,Fshould have offered".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@eO]xD@]OU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
