OL,3,CWireless tickets to go on sale after
OL,4,Cpromoter defends Kanye West appearance
OL,6,FResponding to Mr Benn's statement,
OL,7,FPhil Rosenberg said: "After a week of
OL,8,FWireless Festival avoiding any media,
OL,9,Fthis statement will not reassure many
OL,10,Fwithin the Jewish or other communities
OL,11,Fagainst whom Kanye West's invective
OL,12,Fwas directed over a much longer period
OL,13,Fthan his more recent apology.
OL,15,F"The two key facts remain that Kanye
OL,16,FWest proclaimed himself a Nazi, and
OL,17,Fthat Wireless stands to benefit
OL,18,Ffinancially from his performance.
OL,26,@oD@VOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
