CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775559585
OL,3,CWireless tickets to go on sale after
OL,4,Cpromoter defends Kanye West appearance
OL,6,F"Indeed, we note that concern was Mr
OL,7,FBenn's initial reaction to the idea of
OL,8,Finviting Kanye West. It remains ours.
OL,10,F"Kanye West may well be on the path to
OL,11,Fhealth and healing. We sincerely hope
OL,12,Fthat he is. But the space to test this
OL,13,Fis not over three days on the Wireless
OL,14,Fmain stage."
OL,16,FShadow home secretary Chris Philp said
OL,17,FWest was "guilty of appalling
OL,18,Fantisemitic and pro-Nazi comments" as
OL,19,Fhe urged Ms Mahmood to use her powers
OL,20,Funder the Immigration Act to refuse
OL,21,Fhim a visa.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@LO]yD@JOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
