OL,3,CWireless tickets to go on sale after
OL,4,Cpromoter defends Kanye West appearance
OL,6,FPepsi and Diageo withdrew their
OL,7,Fsponsorship of the festival after West
OL,8,Fwas announced as the headline act, and
OL,9,Fno brands appeared as visible sponsors
OL,10,Fon Wireless Festival's official
OL,11,Fwebsite on Monday evening.
OL,13,FAn AB InBev spokesperson said, in
OL,14,Fregard to Budweiser and Beatbox: "We
OL,15,Fhave decided to withdraw our
OL,16,Fsponsorship of this year's Wireless
OL,17,FFestival."
OL,26,@vD@bOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
