OL,3,CWireless tickets to go on sale after
OL,4,Cpromoter defends Kanye West appearance
OL,6,FAdditionally PayPal, which is a
OL,7,Fpayment partner for the annual rap and
OL,8,Fhip-hop festival, will not appear in
OL,9,Fany of its future promotional
OL,10,Fmaterials, the Press Association
OL,11,Funderstands.
OL,13,FWest, who has not performed in the UK
OL,14,Fsince he headlined Glastonbury in
OL,15,F2015, has drawn widespread criticism
OL,16,Fin recent years after he began voicing
OL,17,Fadmiration for Adolf Hitler, and has
OL,18,Fmade a series of antisemitic remarks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
