OL,3,CWireless tickets to go on sale after
OL,4,Cpromoter defends Kanye West appearance
OL,6,FLast year he released a song called
OL,7,FHeil Hitler, a few months after
OL,8,Fadvertising a swastika T-shirt for
OL,9,Fsale on his website.
OL,11,FThe musician has been barred from X
OL,12,Fbecause of antisemitism on multiple
OL,13,Foccasions.
OL,15,FIt is understood that the mayor of
OL,16,FLondon's office refused permission for
OL,17,Fthe London Stadium, in Stratford, to
OL,18,Fstage a Kanye West concert this
OL,19,Fsummer, with sources citing community
OL,20,Fconcerns and the reputational impact
OL,21,Fon the city.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
