OL,3,CWireless tickets to go on sale after
OL,4,Cpromoter defends Kanye West appearance
OL,6,FThe 48-year-old rapper's scheduled
OL,7,Fappearance comes amid fears of growing
OL,8,Fantisemitism in the UK.
OL,10,FIn March, four ambulances from a
OL,11,FJewish community-run service were set
OL,12,Fon fire in north-west London.
OL,14,FTwo men and a 17-year-old boy were
OL,15,Fremanded in custody on Saturday after
OL,16,Fappearing in court accused of torching
OL,17,Fthe vehicles.
OL,19,FIn October last year, two men were
OL,20,Fkilled in an attack on a Manchester
OL,21,Fsynagogue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
