OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775559585
OL,3,CWireless tickets to go on sale after
OL,4,Cpromoter defends Kanye West appearance
OL,6,FIn January, West took out a full-page
OL,7,Fadvert in the Wall Street Journal to
OL,8,Fapologise, titled: "To Those I've
OL,9,FHurt."
OL,11,F"I am not a Nazi or an antisemite," it
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"I love Jewish people."
OL,16,FIn his letter, he said his bipolar
OL,17,Fdisorder led him to fall into "a four-
OL,18,Fmonth-long, manic episode of
OL,19,Fpsychotic, paranoid and impulsive
OL,20,Fbehaviour that destroyed my life".
